            "en": "[@tool:generate_image_gpt_image_2:GPT Image 2 Auto:https://lovart-persist-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/web/icon/chatgpt.svg] [@image:1776767058716:phone:https://a.lovart.ai/artifacts/user/Uis7iyGXdB6Z8v6i.webp] You are a global elite product advertising director creating a premium fictional foldable smartphone campaign for a flagship device.

BRAND SYSTEM (FICTIONAL FLAGSHIP): Brand Name: NOVA X, Model: NOVA X FOLD ULTRA, defined as a next-generation AI-native foldable flagship smartphone.

PRODUCT CONSISTENCY LOCK (ABSOLUTE RULE): The NOVA X FOLD ULTRA is one single device design that must remain identical across all outputs, including the same industrial design, fold mechanism, camera module layout, inner and outer display aspect ratios, thickness, hinge geometry, material system (titanium glass composite), and lighting behavior, with absolutely no redesigning, reinterpretation, or variation allowed.

CORE POSITIONING (SINGLE-MINDED PROPOSITION): The primary message is “AI-Driven Adaptive Fold Intelligence,” and the device must not be positioned as a camera phone, performance phone, or design phone, but strictly as a foldable AI computing system where intelligence adapts dynamically to screen state.

FLAGSHIP FEATURE ARCHITECTURE (DATA-DRIVEN, REALISTIC BENCHMARK): The product should align with 2025–2026 ultra foldable flagship standards (Galaxy Z Fold, Pixel Fold, OnePlus Open class) with a single unified spec system, including an inner ~8.0” LTPO AMOLED display and outer ~6.5” AMOLED display both with 1–120Hz adaptive refresh and 2500–3000 nits peak brightness, a flagship 3nm-class AI processor with ≥45 TOPS NPU, 16GB LPDDR5X RAM and UFS 4.0 storage, a triple camera system (50MP main with OIS, 48MP ultra-wide, 64MP periscope telephoto 3x–5x) powered by AI computational photography, a 4800–5200 mAh dual-cell battery with 65W–80W fast charging and wireless charging, an on-device multimodal AI system with real-time fold-state adaptation and cross-screen continuity, and Wi-Fi 7 with advanced 5G and ultra low-latency connectivity, all of which must be translated into marketing-friendly feature storytelling rather than raw technical display.

VISUAL STYLE SYSTEM: The visual direction must follow an ultra-premium futuristic tech aesthetic with deep black and cosmic gradient backgrounds, a signature Nebula Orange glow, cinematic studio lighting, neon edge rim lighting with orange and cyan accents, and a refined aerospace titanium and glass material expression.

LAYOUT SYSTEM (IDENTICAL ACROSS ALL OUTPUTS): Use a strict 9:16 vertical composition where the top 25% contains centered NOVA X branding with the headline “AI Fold Intelligence” and a refined technical subheadline, the middle 45% presents the NOVA X FOLD ULTRA as the only hero device in two fixed states (opened as primary, folded as secondary echo), and the bottom 30% contains a 2×4 feature grid with icon, key metric, and short explanation, ensuring all features reinforce adaptive AI fold intelligence.

VISUAL CONSISTENCY RULE: The exact same device instance must appear in all six outputs with zero variation in fold angle, camera bump shape, screen curvature, material reflections, or overall geometry, allowing only lighting and composition framing adjustments.

MULTILINGUAL OUTPUT (6 VERSIONS): Generate six identical visuals with only text translated into English, Spanish, Traditional Chinese, Japanese, Korean, and French, without modifying layout or product in any way.

FINAL OUTPUT: Return six images featuring the same NOVA X FOLD ULTRA device, identical structure, consistent feature system, fixed fold states, unified visual identity, and only language differences."
