Apparel & Skin Tone Matching Rule: All outfits are precisely derived from the ribbed-knit styles in the uploaded product images. Strict Rule: Women with deep/warm skin tones wear light-colored sets; women with pale/cool skin tones wear deep-colored ribbed sets. No extra or unrelated clothing items.

The Six Full-Body Scenes (Sequence 1-6):

1. (Deep Black skin): A full-body candid shot standing by the weathered brick entrance of a trendy urban cafe, holding a green smoothie and a phone, looking naturally away from the camera.
2. (Pale White skin with blonde hair): A full-body self-mirror shot in a sun-drenched private home space with a cozy chair and plants and flowers in the background. She holds her phone high to capture the entire outfit from head to toe.
