4. (East Asian skin with dark-orange short hair): A full-body candid shot in a bright Pilates studio with wooden floors and reformers. She is captured from a slightly low angle, standing naturally near the equipment.
5. (Latina skin): A full-body candid shot (taken by someone else) in front of a "ins-style" wall of a cafe. She is gracefully holding a small dog (like a toy poodle) in her arms, looking towards the lens.
6. (Two-Person Co-shot - Fair-skinned White & Deep Black skin): > A full-body candid photograph captured in a minimalist, professional Pilates studio with an arched white wall and concrete flooring. Two barefoot women are interacting on and around a wooden Pilates reformer.
* The Fair-skinned White woman (blonde): Standing on the left side of the reformer, she is performing a single-leg balance pose with one leg bent at the knee, smiling naturally towards her friend.
* The Deep Black woman: Sitting cross-legged on the reformer carriage, she is stretching her neck with one hand behind her head and the other resting on the machine.

Technical Details: > Shot with an iPhone 17 Pro rear camera, 4K high-definition quality, crisp and detailed fabric textures. The composition is a full-body shot with a 3:4 aspect ratio. Natural, soft indoor lighting, no text, no borders."
