        {
          "title": {
            "en": "Generate live screenshot"
          },
          "prompt": {
            "en": "[@tool:generate_image_gpt_image_2:GPT Image 2:https://lovart-persist-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/web/icon/chatgpt.svg] [@image:1776784252525:mockup:https://a.lovart.ai/artifacts/user/DN3WPHhkFhDmElt0.png] Generate a hyper-realistic 9:16 vertical smartphone screenshot of a LIVE streaming moment at exact resolution 1080x1920 pixels, replicating a real mobile capture.

CORE PRIORITY (UI REPLICATION): You must strictly replicate the LIVE interface from the provided reference image, which is the only source of truth for UI layout and structure, ensuring pixel-level structural fidelity with no redesign, no reinterpretation, no improvement, and no replacement with generic or updated UI styles.

UI STRUCTURE LOCK: Preserve all layout zones (top, center, bottom), component positions, spacing, alignment, hierarchy, overlay stacking logic, and chat placement exactly as in the reference, with absolutely no layout rearrangement, no added or removed modules, and no platform switching to feed, reels, or hybrid interfaces.

FORMAT CONSTRAINT: The output must be exactly 1080x1920 pixels in a strict 9:16 vertical format, full-bleed edge-to-edge, with no borders, no device frame, no phone mockups, no tablet or desktop UI, and must feel like a real captured smartphone screen.

UI TYPE CONSTRAINT: This must be a pure LIVE streaming room, with no feed, no FYP, no reels, no scrolling lists, no hybrid layouts, no video player UI, and no feed-style right-side stacks.

